| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5825 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 49525bf4-e549-515b-9147-48b86a2f0cfb"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
